window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>When Mr. Right is Mr Oh-so-very-wrong…</b></p> <p>When Ashley leaves a review on a site for adult items, moaning about her husband's lack of interest, she doesn't expect anyone to care. But one man does. He fixates on her and decides to show her exactly how attractive he finds her. The collar she purchased won't go unused. No. She'll become his perfect pet.</p> <p><i>The Hot Creeps novellas are quick, fun, and heat-packed.</i></p>"; 
